title: Late Night Sessions #TBT: Kacey Musgraves
description:
This segment was originally published on July 10, 2018.

Late Night music booker Jeremiah Silva talks to Kacey Musgraves about her album "Golden Hour" and the song "Rainbow," which made its TV debut on Late Night.
